{"tid":2431461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠市長等人有返銀行戶口用了","createTime":"2021-03-03T16:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T16:10:51.000Z","uid":325565,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc18b54c3dce98933fa5ec08481045e152fb66c9","tid":2431461,"uid":325565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"內地兩會舉行在即，多個內地部委、監管機構輪流會見傳媒，中銀保監會主席郭樹清今早表示，<strong><span class=\"red\"><ins>中國銀保監會和中國整個銀行系統不會執行美國法律法規，並指美國制裁毫無約束力，在香港的金融機構，不論中資、外資都要遵守香港的法律法規，不會執行美國所要求制裁。</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2890190/【美國制裁】郭樹清：在港中外金融機構不執行美國制裁%E3%80%80願繼續開放外資進入金融業\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2890190%2F%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E3%80%91%E9%83%AD%E6%A8%B9%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%96%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%25E3%2580%2580%E9%A1%98%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%87%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%A5%AD&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX8IAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=24ff35cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2890190/【美國制裁】郭樹清：在港中外金融機構不執行美國制裁%E3%80%80願繼續開放外資進入金融業</a>"},{"pid":"8a4dc698cf4efc9e0bab90cef704d1a95e8e58f6","tid":2431461,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"你真係唔明佢哋做緊乜咩<br />\n<br />\n叫所有被制裁人士自己刪戶口<br />\n所以嗰個先至咁快還清晒按揭<br />\n<br />\n冇戶口咪唔使制裁囉<br />\n呢個就係佢哋所講唔會執行美方制裁<br />\n<br />\n支那人最叻就係做假<br />\n由頭到腳趾公都係假"},{"pid":"e0d3df5fadbc3e58ec6d3702fb7ab0d9b6f5da3c","tid":2431461,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://nyanswop.org/static/media/logo.baa8a976.png&amp;h=a7478a94&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n病貓：屌又搵著我黎搞"},{"pid":"f3c9228d248540b9d046288d2e79afcce38641a3","tid":2431461,"uid":184371,"like":1,"d